    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you don't implement this method, it returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " by default. If you return "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " from this method, but you don't implement "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverdelegate/1534822-detachablewindowforpopover"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or you implement it to return "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", a detachable window is created with the popoverâ€™s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopover/1526794-contentviewcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "An automatically created window has the same appearance as the detached popover. For example, if the popover's "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopover/1526794-contentviewcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " has a title, it will be bound to and displayed as the title of the detached window. When a popover is released in a detached state, it calls "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverdelegate/1524674-popoverdiddetach"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " on the delegate. When a detached popover is closed, calls to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverdelegate/1532593-popovershouldclose"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverdelegate/1535119-popoverwillclose"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverdelegate/1526581-popoverdidclose"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", in addition to the related notifications, specify the reason "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverclosereasonstandard"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
